{
  "stem": "27335.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and about two weeks-- two weeks later-- later, we found out right from him that he knew some Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And how that-- that we found that out, but he used to work with the Hungarian embassy at-- at one time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they learned some Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's why they put-- put-- on this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But everything was-- was really planned.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was an army barrack for the British, you see, and we went in for-- went in for-- for-- for the intelligence training mostly, as they hear the news.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, it was everything, but all right, you have to watch this and then know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- and--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- well, this one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think it was in the third or four days, we went out with Adam-- Adam was his name, my-- my-- my partner, my Canadian partner-- Muhammed Ali Boulevard, we went out for-- for a-- for a stroll.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nothing else to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't even know where we are going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we were just going into further-- into the city and towards the railway station.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on the Main Street there, we come to-- come to a point where we heard Hungarian voices.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were four-- four boys and one girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- [LAUGHS] We come closer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There are children of Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they were really sharply discussing something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he comes a few steps closer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They started talking about Morse and Langer and Stalin and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so-- so we just came right up to them and greeted in-- greeted them in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[HUNGARIAN] [LAUGHS] Oh, it was so [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there were four boys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And one of the girls that you see-- see here, up on the wall, Hannah [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we just looked at each other.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had four to look at.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
